rows.label: qst101808_msg002
rows.name:
The debt is over 500,000G,
so this is not enough.

rows.label: qst101808_msg003
rows.name: That's ridiculous, mo.

rows.label: qst101808_msg004
rows.name: Let's negotiate directly, mo.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0001
rows.name: Yo! Possah! Long time no see.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0002
rows.name:
Vahsah! ...You're the
one from the other day.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0003
rows.name: Are you really Jizo?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0004
rows.name: Umo...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0005
rows.name: *stare* *staaaaare* *staaaaaaaaare*

rows.label: qst101808_msg0006
rows.name: Vahsah... Do you remember Possah, mo?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0007
rows.name:
I'd never forget. You're
the one my Driver likes.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0008
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Ah! Ah!! That's a secret, mo~!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0009
rows.name:
You're not short and chubby, and
fluffy and puffy anymore, but...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0010
rows.name: Jizo... Jizo, mo...! Welcome back, mo!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0011
rows.name: I-I'm home, mo, Possah!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0012
rows.name: All's well that ends well.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0013
rows.name:
If Vahsah hadn't gotten into debt,
we could have met sooner...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0014
rows.name:
Mo~ Did Vahsah cause trouble
for Jizo again, mo?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0015
rows.name:
It's okay, mo~ I made
it back safely, mo.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0016
rows.name: Everyone, thank you so much, mo!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0017
rows.name: I don't know how to thank you...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0018
rows.name:
Everyone is happy, mo! I hope
you'll be happy too, mo~

rows.label: qst101808_msg0019
rows.name:
Well, Jizo! First, let's
take a bath and get you
all fluffy and puffy, mo!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0020
rows.name: Okay, mo~ Well then, see you again, mo~
